data.description: Welcome to your charming Ranch-style retreat in the serene town of York Springs, offering effortless commutes to both the vibrant Gettysburg area and bustling Harrisburg. This delightful abode boasts three cozy bedrooms, perfect for peaceful slumbers, accompanied by a full bathroom with a stall shower for your comfort. Step inside to discover the timeless allure of solid hardwood floors, guiding you through each inviting space with elegance and warmth. The heart of the home beckons with an enclosed sunroom, providing the ideal setting for morning coffees or evening relaxation, enveloped by the tranquil beauty of your surroundings. For the automotive enthusiast or DIY aficionado, an oversized two-bay garage stands ready to accommodate your vehicles and projects, ensuring ample space for storage and creativity to flourish. Additionally, a bonus garage bay in the basement presents limitless possibilities for customization and convenience. Embrace the joys of outdoor living on the expansive 1.19-acre lot, offering picturesque views of pastoral landscapes that inspire a sense of peace and tranquility. Whether you envision lively gatherings under the open sky or moments of quiet contemplation amidst nature's embrace, this generous parcel of land provides the canvas for your dreams to unfold. Seize this opportunity to embrace a lifestyle of comfort, convenience, and connection in a cherished locale where the best of both worlds awaits. Don't miss your chance to make this idyllic retreat your own and experience the quintessential charm of country living, mere moments from urban amenities.
